Kieffer's Performance List (TFRRS)

2022-23 • Sophomore

Cross Country

• Competed in the Billiken Invitational and Loyola Lakefront Invitational.

• PR'd in both meets, posting a 5K time of 22:56.6 at the Billiken Invitational and a 6K time of 27:26.9 at Loyola.

Indoor Track and Field

• Competed in a variety of middle distance and relay events for the Bills.

• Won the 600 yards at the ISU Classic with a time of 1:29.58.

• Ran legs on Billikens' top relay squads in the 4x400, 4x800 and Distance Medley relays.

• Competed at the A-10 Championships in the 500 meters and 4x800-meter relay.

Outdoor Track and Field

• Was the Billikens' top performer in the 800 meters with a top time of 2:21.45 at the Kip Janvrin Open.

• Ran the third leg on the Billikens' 4x400-meter relay that placed fourth at the prestigious Drake Relays.

• Anchored the Billikens 4x800-meter relay team at the A-10 Championships.

• Also competed in the 800 meters at the A-10s.

2021-22 • Freshman

Cross Country

• Ran in the Gans Creek Classic and Bradley Pink Classic.

• Had a top 6K time of 27:39.1 at the Bradley Pink Classic.

Indoor Track and Field

• Ran relays and middle distance events for the Billikens.

• Competed in three events at the A-10 Championships.

• SLU’s top competitor in the 500 meters, running a PR of 1:21.02 at the A-10 Championships.

• Finished second in the 800 meters at the John Coughlan Invitational.

Outdoor Track and Field

• Competed in the 400 meters and 800 meters as well as relay events for the Billikens.

• Top 400-meter time of 1:00.90 came at the Kip Janvrin Open.

• Had a PR in the 800 meters of 2:20.59 at the Kentucky Invitational.

• Ran a leg on the Billikens’ 4x800-meter relay team that just missed scoring at the A-10 Championships with a ninth-place finish.

2020-21 • Freshman

Cross Country

• Did not compete.

Indoor Track and Field

• Season not held due to COVID-19.

Outdoor Track and Field

• Competed in the 800 meters and 1,500 meters.

• Registered a top 800-meter time of 2:29.91 at the Sycamore Open.

• Ran the 1,500 meters in 5:30.23 at the Billiken Invitational.
